Package com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.msg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClusterStatusMessage
    POJO used to exchange information on status of the cluster; that is, settings for nodes that are known by a given server node.
    ExtensibleType
    Base class used by those message types that need to be able to evolve and survive cases of "new client sending new stuff" that can occur during upgrades.
    ListItem
    Full result entry contained in ExtensibleType (as an alternative to ids, StorableKey).
    ListResponse<T>
    Response message type for List requests.
    ListResponse.IdListResponse  
    ListResponse.MinimalItemListResponse  
    ListResponse.NameListResponse
